:"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9682a71d1304ab628a14cfbb41a35d06_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1743126407.190873","card_id":"Q_14827234820","target":{"id":14827234820,"title":"连云港相比青岛港口位置更好，为何经济发展不如青岛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14827234820","type":"question","created":1741831933,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":73,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3306,4592,11011,102410],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"连云港背靠陇海路，被誉为亚欧大陆桥头堡，经济腹地非常广阔，关中中原地区以及苏北皖北距离最近的出海口就是连云港。反观青岛，仅仅是山东一省的良港，为何经济发展和城市地位远超连云港？"},"attached_info":"CkEIm8mE79WqkPIuEAMaCTExMzk0NjExOCD9/ci+BjAAOElAHHILMTQ4MjcyMzQ4MjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"54 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-30c8aa18bc1295ca3abbf8eba0cf513a_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1743126407.191329","card_id":"Q_665731716","target":{"id":665731716,"title":"为什么transformer的FFN需要先升维再降维？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665731716","type":"question","created":1725016761,"answer_count":20,"follower_count":326,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3279,372847,401598,3024391],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"W_2矩阵一般是4d\\times d的，那么它的rank最高为d，也就是说至少有3d行可以被其他行线性表出，假设某个inputx\\in R^{1\\times d}在经过W_1以及激活函数后的hidden state为h\\in R^{1\\times 4d}那么FFN的outputh\\cdot W_2可以看作是对W_2的4d行进行一个加权求和\\sum_{i=1}^{4d}{h_i}W_{2,i}，其中h_i代表h的第i个分量，W_{2,i}代表W_2的第i行。由于W_2的低秩特性，我总可以在W_2找到n(n\\leq d)个线性无关的行(假设就是前n行)，从而对于任意1\\leq i\\leq 4d，W_{2,i}都可以由这n行线性表出W_{2,i}=\\sum_{j=1}^{n}{c_j}W_{2,j}，所以上述加权求和总可以进行改写：\\sum_{i=1}^{4d}{h_i}W_{2,i}=\\sum_{i=1}^{n}{k_i}W_{2,i}，那么W_2矩阵只需要这n行即可，模型只需要学习到如何通过W_1和激活函数来得到“新的”h'\\in R^{1\\times n}=\\{k_1, k_2,...,k_n\\}，那么这么看完全不需要现在的FFN中先升维再降维的操作，所以为什么降低FFN中矩阵的维度实践中往往效果会变差呢？"},"attached_info":"CkAIm8mE79WqkPIuEAMaCTExMDIxNzk0OCC51ca2BjAAOMYCQB1yCTY2NTczMTcxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"54 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b7ade636138b3d7a3dab6ba84f3e95c6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]}],"description":{"time":"2025-03-28 09:46:47"}}